n   SPACE + m       -> show dap guide
n   m + b           -> toggle breakpoint line
n   m + l           -> list breakpoints
n   m + o           -> clear breakpoints
n   m + c           -> run/continue
n   m + p           -> pause
n   m + t           -> close (terminate)
n   m + n           -> step over
n   m + s           -> step into
n   m + f           -> step out (finish)
n   m + z           -> run to cursor
n   m + r           -> open/close repl
n   m + k           -> toggle hover
